        "body": "## Changes\r\n- Added missing translation keys for:\r\n  - **Polygon tools** (`breakPolygon`, `convertToPolygon`)\r\n  - **General UI** (`tab`, `shapeSwitch`)\r\n  - **Library & Search** (`inputPlaceholder`, `heading`, `noResults`, `clearSearch`)\r\n  - **Buttons** (`saveLibNames`, `publishLibrary`)\r\n  - **Alerts** (`localStorageQuotaExceeded`)\r\n  - **Toolbar** (`lasso`, `convertElementType`)\r\n  - **Hints** (Added various missing shortcuts and tool hints)\r\n  - **Color Picker** (`color`)\r\n  - **Keyboard Shortcuts** (`keys` section)\r\n- Updated existing keys to ensure parity with the English ([en.json](cci:7://file:///Users/aniruddhsharma/Desktop/excaliDraw%20pr/excalidraw/packages/excalidraw/locales/en.json:0:0-0:0)) locale.\r\n\r\n## Type of change\r\n- [x] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\r\n- [ ] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\r\n- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to not work as expected)\r\n- [x] Translation update\r\n\r\n## How Has This Been Tested?\r\n- Validated the JSON structure of [mr-IN.json](cci:7://file:///Users/aniruddhsharma/Desktop/excaliDraw%20pr/excalidraw/packages/excalidraw/locales/mr-IN.json:0:0-0:0).\r\n- Verified that the keys match the English locale file (`en.json`).",
